    "On the other hand, his work means that the age of quantum computers may come sooner.",
    "This has sparked a frenzy of research into post-quantum cryptography (PQC), among the four main areas in post-quantum research (Multivariate, code-based, hash-based, and lattice-based), latticebased cryptography is undoubtedly the most concerned because it is based on the mathematically rigorous computational problems which lead to reliable and verifiable.",
